TI  - SleepSynth: Evaluating the use of Synthetic Data in Health Digital Twins
AU  - Kumi, Sandra
AU  - Hilton, Maxwell
AU  - Snow, Charles
AU  - Lomotey, Richard K.
AU  - Deters, Ralph
