TI  - AI-Driven Generative Modeling and Optimization for Ethical and Scalable Selection Systems: A Multi-Domain Scoping Review
AU  - Benjilali, Khadija
AU  - El-Ibrahimi, Abdeljalil
AU  - Moutaouakil, Wassima
AU  - Hamida, Soufiane
