TI  - Lung Ultrasound Findings and Algorithms to Detect Pneumonia: A Systematic Review and Diagnostic Testing Meta-Analysis.
AU  - Padrao, Eduardo Messias Hirano
AU  - Caldeira Antonio, Bruno
AU  - Gardner, Tiffany Alexis
AU  - Miyawaki, Isabele Ayumi
AU  - Gomes, Cintia
AU  - Riceto Loyola Junior, Jose Eduardo
