TI  - Emerging Technologies and Algorithms for Periodontal Screening and Risk of Disease Progression in Non-Dental Settings: A Scoping Review.
AU  - Montero, Eduardo
AU  - Sánchez, Nerea
AU  - Sanz-Sánchez, Ignacio
AU  - López-Durán, Mercedes
AU  - de Albornoz, Ana Carrillo
